{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/blog/2022/zsh-prompt-custom/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"1e8983d1-900e-5568-9b10-b0ea47c8a1b8","excerpt":"プラグインを入れずにカスタマイズをする。 基本 まず、プロンプトのカスタマイズは.zshrcなどでPROMPT…","html":"<p>プラグインを入れずにカスタマイズをする。</p>\n<h2 id=\"基本\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC\" aria-label=\"基本 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline; fill: #57606a;\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>基本</h2>\n<p>まず、プロンプトのカスタマイズは<code>.zshrc</code>などで<code>PROMPT</code>などに値を代入することで行える</p>\n<p>試しに</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"bash\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk3\"># .zshrc</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">PROMPT=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;$&quot;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>とすると</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c987250235266523d660d7cdefbaf81c/776d3/terminal_%24.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 18.354430379746837%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAECAYAAACOXx+WAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAANklEQVR42mNQ01P5r6ak+l9dBTtWU1b5r6Oh+V9PS/u/GoiPhNVV1KAYoZ6BgYHhP5XxIDcQANPgWJF8JGkzAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"$のみ\"\n        title=\"$のみ\"\n        src=\"/static/c987250235266523d660d7cdefbaf81c/f058b/terminal_%24.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c987250235266523d660d7cdefbaf81c/c26ae/terminal_%24.png 158w,\n/static/c987250235266523d660d7cdefbaf81c/6bdcf/terminal_%24.png 315w,\n/static/c987250235266523d660d7cdefbaf81c/f058b/terminal_%24.png 630w,\n/static/c987250235266523d660d7cdefbaf81c/40601/terminal_%24.png 945w,\n/static/c987250235266523d660d7cdefbaf81c/78612/terminal_%24.png 1260w,\n/static/c987250235266523d660d7cdefbaf81c/776d3/terminal_%24.png 1814w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>のようになり、またさらに以下のようにすると</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"bash\" data-index=\"1\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk3\"># .zshrc</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">PROMPT=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;$&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">RPROMPT=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;///&quot;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bcae8831f66b2526924def85abb24047/776d3/terminal_%24slash.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 18.354430379746837%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAECAYAAACOXx+WAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAOUlEQVR42mNQ01P5r6ak+l9dBTtWU1b5r6Oh+V9PS/u/GoiPhNVV1KAYql5V7T8DAwPDfyrjQW4gANXLWJM+UUl+AAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"$と///\"\n        title=\"$と///\"\n        src=\"/static/bcae8831f66b2526924def85abb24047/f058b/terminal_%24slash.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bcae8831f66b2526924def85abb24047/c26ae/terminal_%24slash.png 158w,\n/static/bcae8831f66b2526924def85abb24047/6bdcf/terminal_%24slash.png 315w,\n/static/bcae8831f66b2526924def85abb24047/f058b/terminal_%24slash.png 630w,\n/static/bcae8831f66b2526924def85abb24047/40601/terminal_%24slash.png 945w,\n/static/bcae8831f66b2526924def85abb24047/78612/terminal_%24slash.png 1260w,\n/static/bcae8831f66b2526924def85abb24047/776d3/terminal_%24slash.png 1814w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>となる(左に<code>///</code>が追加された)。</p>\n<h3 id=\"僕のプロンプト\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%83%95%E3%81%AE%E3%83%97%E3%83%AD%E3%83%B3%E3%83%97%E3%83%88\" aria-label=\"僕のプロンプト permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline; fill: #57606a;\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>僕のプロンプト</h3>\n<p>僕はできる限りシンプルにしたかったので、以下のような見た目になっている。<br>\n(普段はこれに tmux を起動して、その他の情報を載せてたりする)</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/24def/terminal_my.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 15.18987341772152%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAYAAACTWi8uAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAATElEQVR42mMw01b4r6Kt8F9BVv6/ghwmlpeV+6+spPRfRUkJzMamBoLl/isrKv5nEJYQ+M/DxfKfgYGBYszIyPifgZmFeoYxMTH9BwBFPUPAY6IORwAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"スクリーンショット 2022-04-03 18.03.57.png\"\n        title=\"スクリーンショット 2022-04-03 18.03.57.png\"\n        src=\"/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/f058b/terminal_my.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/c26ae/terminal_my.png 158w,\n/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/6bdcf/terminal_my.png 315w,\n/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/f058b/terminal_my.png 630w,\n/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/40601/terminal_my.png 945w,\n/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/78612/terminal_my.png 1260w,\n/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/24def/terminal_my.png 1812w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>これの設定ファイルは下に折りたたんだ。この説明は最後で行う。</p>\n<details>\n  <summary>設定ファイル</summary>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"bash\" data-index=\"2\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk11\">left-prompt</span><span class=\"mtk1\">() {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk4\">local</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> dir=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;%F{11}%~%f&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk4\">local</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> next=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;%F{47}❯%f &quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk11\">echo</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> -e </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;\\n</span><span class=\"mtk12\">${user}${dir}</span><span class=\"mtk8\">\\n</span><span class=\"mtk12\">${next}</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk11\">right-prompt</span><span class=\"mtk1\">() {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk4\">local</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> time=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;%F{242}%T%f&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk11\">echo</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk12\">${time}</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">PROMPT=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">`left-prompt`</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">RPROMPT=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">`right-prompt`</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk11\">unset</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> -f left-prompt</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk11\">unset</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> -f right-prompt</span></span></span></code></pre>\n</details>\n<h2 id=\"情報の追加\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E3%81%AE%E8%BF%BD%E5%8A%A0\" aria-label=\"情報の追加 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline; fill: #57606a;\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>情報の追加</h2>\n<p>現在のディレクトリと時間を表示するためには<code>%~</code>と<code>%T</code>を用いると表示できる。</p>\n<p>例えば</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"bash\" data-index=\"3\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">PROMPT=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;%~ &gt; &quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">RPROMPT=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;%T&quot;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>とすると、</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/827801fb310f01e0ff4812f5d3e5c2f3/24def/terminal_info.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 15.18987341772152%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAYAAACTWi8uAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAR0lEQVR42mOwNdL8r6Gv/l9XS+e/sqLif3lZuf8KcvJwDOIrKyn9V1FSwpBDVgOS19HS/s/AwMAAIv6zsLD8h7EpxAz/qYkBdo1D16deGWcAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"スクリーンショット 2022-04-03 18.04.19.png\"\n        title=\"スクリーンショット 2022-04-03 18.04.19.png\"\n        src=\"/static/827801fb310f01e0ff4812f5d3e5c2f3/f058b/terminal_info.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/827801fb310f01e0ff4812f5d3e5c2f3/c26ae/terminal_info.png 158w,\n/static/827801fb310f01e0ff4812f5d3e5c2f3/6bdcf/terminal_info.png 315w,\n/static/827801fb310f01e0ff4812f5d3e5c2f3/f058b/terminal_info.png 630w,\n/static/827801fb310f01e0ff4812f5d3e5c2f3/40601/terminal_info.png 945w,\n/static/827801fb310f01e0ff4812f5d3e5c2f3/78612/terminal_info.png 1260w,\n/static/827801fb310f01e0ff4812f5d3e5c2f3/24def/terminal_info.png 1812w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>のようになる。</p>\n<p>下の表は<a href=\"https://tegetegekibaru.blogspot.com/2012/08/zsh_2.html\">https://tegetegekibaru.blogspot.com/2012/08/zsh_2.html</a>より、そのままコピペさせていただいた。上の例のようにパラメータを<code>PROMPT</code>などに渡せば良い</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>パラメータ</th>\n<th>出力内容</th>\n<th>例</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>%M</td>\n<td>ホスト名</td>\n<td>localhost.localdomain</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%m</td>\n<td>ホスト名</td>\n<td>localhost</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%n</td>\n<td>ユーザ名</td>\n<td>root</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%#</td>\n<td>ユーザ種別</td>\n<td>#（root の場合） %（root 以外）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%y</td>\n<td>ログイン端末名</td>\n<td>pts/0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%l</td>\n<td>ログイン端末名</td>\n<td>pst/0（tty*の場合は tty を省略）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%?</td>\n<td>直前のコマンドの戻り値</td>\n<td>0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%h %!</td>\n<td>コマンド実行数 （history 数）</td>\n<td>1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%d %/</td>\n<td>カレントディレクトリ</td>\n<td>/root/currentdir</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%~</td>\n<td>カレントディレクトリ</td>\n<td>~/currentdir</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%C</td>\n<td>カレントディレクトリ</td>\n<td>currentdir</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%c %.</td>\n<td>カレントディレクトリ</td>\n<td>currentdir （$PWD=$HOME の場合は~）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%D</td>\n<td>日付</td>\n<td>12-07-31 (yy-mm-dd)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%W</td>\n<td>日付</td>\n<td>07/31/12 (mm/dd/yy)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%w</td>\n<td>日付</td>\n<td>Sun 31 (day dd)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%*</td>\n<td>時間</td>\n<td>15:50:30 (hh:mm:ss)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%T</td>\n<td>時間</td>\n<td>15:50 (hh:mm)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%t %@</td>\n<td>時間</td>\n<td>03:50PM (hh:mm(am/pm format))</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"装飾\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%A3%85%E9%A3%BE\" aria-label=\"装飾 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline; fill: #57606a;\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>装飾</h2>\n<p>ただの白文字ではつまらないので装飾したい。</p>\n<h3 id=\"色\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%89%B2\" aria-label=\"色 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline; fill: #57606a;\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>色</h3>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"bash\" data-index=\"4\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">%F{色番号}色をつける内容%f</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>とすると色がつけられる。\nつまり<code>%F</code>と<code>%fで</code>囲われたところに色がつく。色はターミナルの 256 色(0~255)で指定する。</p>\n<p>例えば</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"bash\" data-index=\"5\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">PROMPT=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;%F{45}%~%f &gt; &quot;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>とすると</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/648baa509a5cdd21ccb5bb1477389577/776d3/terminal_color.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 18.354430379746837%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAECAYAAACOXx+WAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAASUlEQVR42mNQN9f7r6Ku/V/fwOC/tqbWf1Vllf9qKqpwDOJraWhilUPFEDkGBhaO/wxs7P/ZObn+MzMz/WdgYKAUM/ynMqaugQBI1Vj8Ad7yHQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"color\"\n        title=\"color\"\n        src=\"/static/648baa509a5cdd21ccb5bb1477389577/f058b/terminal_color.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/648baa509a5cdd21ccb5bb1477389577/c26ae/terminal_color.png 158w,\n/static/648baa509a5cdd21ccb5bb1477389577/6bdcf/terminal_color.png 315w,\n/static/648baa509a5cdd21ccb5bb1477389577/f058b/terminal_color.png 630w,\n/static/648baa509a5cdd21ccb5bb1477389577/40601/terminal_color.png 945w,\n/static/648baa509a5cdd21ccb5bb1477389577/78612/terminal_color.png 1260w,\n/static/648baa509a5cdd21ccb5bb1477389577/776d3/terminal_color.png 1814w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>色番号の一覧は次の ruby スクリプトを実行することで見れる。(このスクリプトは数年前にどっかで拾った)</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"ruby\" data-index=\"6\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk3\"># -*- coding: utf-8 -*-</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk12\">@fg</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk6\">\\x1b</span><span class=\"mtk8\">[38;5;&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk12\">@bg</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk6\">\\x1b</span><span class=\"mtk8\">[48;5;&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk12\">@rs</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk6\">\\x1b</span><span class=\"mtk8\">[0m&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk15\">def</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">color</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">code</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  number = </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;%3d&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> % code</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">#{</span><span class=\"mtk12\">@bg</span><span class=\"mtk4\">}#{</span><span class=\"mtk1\">code</span><span class=\"mtk4\">}</span><span class=\"mtk8\">m </span><span class=\"mtk4\">#{</span><span class=\"mtk1\">number</span><span class=\"mtk4\">}#{</span><span class=\"mtk12\">@rs</span><span class=\"mtk4\">}#{</span><span class=\"mtk12\">@fg</span><span class=\"mtk4\">}#{</span><span class=\"mtk1\">code</span><span class=\"mtk4\">}</span><span class=\"mtk8\">m </span><span class=\"mtk4\">#{</span><span class=\"mtk1\">number</span><span class=\"mtk4\">}#{</span><span class=\"mtk12\">@rs</span><span class=\"mtk4\">}</span><span class=\"mtk8\"> &quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk15\">end</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">256</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.times </span><span class=\"mtk15\">do</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> |</span><span class=\"mtk12\">n</span><span class=\"mtk1\">|</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk11\">print</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> color(n)</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk11\">print</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk6\">\\n</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk15\">if</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> (n + </span><span class=\"mtk7\">1</span><span class=\"mtk1\">).modulo(</span><span class=\"mtk7\">8</span><span class=\"mtk1\">).zero?</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk15\">end</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk11\">print</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk6\">\\n</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b85a410e914d68436d6a06c7aff7938c/6ee58/256color.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 78.48101265822784%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"256color-list\"\n        title=\"256color-list\"\n        src=\"/static/b85a410e914d68436d6a06c7aff7938c/f058b/256color.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b85a410e914d68436d6a06c7aff7938c/c26ae/256color.png 158w,\n/static/b85a410e914d68436d6a06c7aff7938c/6bdcf/256color.png 315w,\n/static/b85a410e914d68436d6a06c7aff7938c/f058b/256color.png 630w,\n/static/b85a410e914d68436d6a06c7aff7938c/40601/256color.png 945w,\n/static/b85a410e914d68436d6a06c7aff7938c/78612/256color.png 1260w,\n/static/b85a410e914d68436d6a06c7aff7938c/6ee58/256color.png 1640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"太文字\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%A4%AA%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97\" aria-label=\"太文字 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline; fill: #57606a;\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>太文字</h3>\n<p><code>%B</code>と<code>%b</code>で囲う</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d7320959a08ae938827e81db096280f2/8bb81/terminal_colorb.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 16.455696202531648%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAYAAACTWi8uAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAZElEQVR42p3LuwqDUBRE0YlISoWbpMo5itfggxQ+Cv//z7aIhJAmoMUq9sBoXgZ8mYivlnmc6JrIuzf61ukapyoNt6/CjLqKFOY/+4eUP9D9yTXLuYWAJNJUJMlu60MuOnH6YwXch0RtaJJ/mQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"太文字\"\n        title=\"太文字\"\n        src=\"/static/d7320959a08ae938827e81db096280f2/f058b/terminal_colorb.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d7320959a08ae938827e81db096280f2/c26ae/terminal_colorb.png 158w,\n/static/d7320959a08ae938827e81db096280f2/6bdcf/terminal_colorb.png 315w,\n/static/d7320959a08ae938827e81db096280f2/f058b/terminal_colorb.png 630w,\n/static/d7320959a08ae938827e81db096280f2/40601/terminal_colorb.png 945w,\n/static/d7320959a08ae938827e81db096280f2/78612/terminal_colorb.png 1260w,\n/static/d7320959a08ae938827e81db096280f2/8bb81/terminal_colorb.png 1602w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"下線\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%B8%8B%E7%B7%9A\" aria-label=\"下線 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline; fill: #57606a;\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>下線</h3>\n<p><code>%U</code>と<code>%u</code>で囲う</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c6a00b02bfcbf8158a7dce40217b5850/8bb81/terminal_coloru.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 16.455696202531648%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAYAAACTWi8uAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAY0lEQVR42p3LvQqDQBRE4YlCSoVNihT3Kq74k4AQ1/d/tiNBJKQJaPEVZ2CUlglPE7HtSe+ZsY+8RuM5OEPnNLXh9lWZ0TaRyvxn30nlHYUH16LkFgKSyHORZZtPH3LRidMfK8Z4RFLP4PvoAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"下線\"\n        title=\"下線\"\n        src=\"/static/c6a00b02bfcbf8158a7dce40217b5850/f058b/terminal_coloru.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c6a00b02bfcbf8158a7dce40217b5850/c26ae/terminal_coloru.png 158w,\n/static/c6a00b02bfcbf8158a7dce40217b5850/6bdcf/terminal_coloru.png 315w,\n/static/c6a00b02bfcbf8158a7dce40217b5850/f058b/terminal_coloru.png 630w,\n/static/c6a00b02bfcbf8158a7dce40217b5850/40601/terminal_coloru.png 945w,\n/static/c6a00b02bfcbf8158a7dce40217b5850/78612/terminal_coloru.png 1260w,\n/static/c6a00b02bfcbf8158a7dce40217b5850/8bb81/terminal_coloru.png 1602w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"背景色\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E8%89%B2\" aria-label=\"背景色 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline; fill: #57606a;\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>背景色</h3>\n<p><code>%S%F</code>と<code>%f%s</code>で囲う。(<code>%S</code>と<code>%s</code>をつける)</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/09531ac4c244da05377e140e9611f414/8bb81/terminal_colors.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 16.455696202531648%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAYAAACTWi8uAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAaklEQVR42p3LsQrCQBRE0dkspNQi7Xsru2LWiBDJDyiksrG38/9/4gqCBBtBi1PcgdE0n/H5QhmOTOOJ2hcOe2OoTt05eWO4LZIZ21xI5h/7m3S9o9uDNvd06xWSiFE0jQhBr/5J0B+nL57C/kXFQQLuNgAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"背景\"\n        title=\"背景\"\n        src=\"/static/09531ac4c244da05377e140e9611f414/f058b/terminal_colors.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/09531ac4c244da05377e140e9611f414/c26ae/terminal_colors.png 158w,\n/static/09531ac4c244da05377e140e9611f414/6bdcf/terminal_colors.png 315w,\n/static/09531ac4c244da05377e140e9611f414/f058b/terminal_colors.png 630w,\n/static/09531ac4c244da05377e140e9611f414/40601/terminal_colors.png 945w,\n/static/09531ac4c244da05377e140e9611f414/78612/terminal_colors.png 1260w,\n/static/09531ac4c244da05377e140e9611f414/8bb81/terminal_colors.png 1602w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"わかりやすく設定する\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E3%82%8F%E3%81%8B%E3%82%8A%E3%82%84%E3%81%99%E3%81%8F%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B\" aria-label=\"わかりやすく設定する permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline; fill: #57606a;\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>わかりやすく設定する</h2>\n<p>エスケープ文字を使って PROMPT を設定するの読みにくい。<br>\n変数や関数を用いてわかりやすくすると良いと思う。</p>\n<p>僕の設定を再掲する。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/24def/terminal_my.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 15.18987341772152%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAYAAACTWi8uAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAATElEQVR42mMw01b4r6Kt8F9BVv6/ghwmlpeV+6+spPRfRUkJzMamBoLl/isrKv5nEJYQ+M/DxfKfgYGBYszIyPifgZmFeoYxMTH9BwBFPUPAY6IORwAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"僕の\"\n        title=\"僕の\"\n        src=\"/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/f058b/terminal_my.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/c26ae/terminal_my.png 158w,\n/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/6bdcf/terminal_my.png 315w,\n/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/f058b/terminal_my.png 630w,\n/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/40601/terminal_my.png 945w,\n/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/78612/terminal_my.png 1260w,\n/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/24def/terminal_my.png 1812w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><code>local</code>をつけると変数のスコープを制限できるので zsh が汚れず良い。<br>\n<code>left-prompt()</code>と<code>right-prompt()</code>の関数を用いることで<code>PROMPT</code>, <code>RPROMPT</code>の意味がわかりやすくなる。<br>\n関数の返り値の扱いは<code>echo</code>と<code>`function`</code>を使ってる人がいたので真似した(あってるの?)</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"bash\" data-index=\"7\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk11\">left-prompt</span><span class=\"mtk1\">() {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk4\">local</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> dir=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;%F{11}%~%f&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk4\">local</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> next=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;%F{47}❯%f &quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk11\">echo</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> -e </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;\\n</span><span class=\"mtk12\">${user}${dir}</span><span class=\"mtk8\">\\n</span><span class=\"mtk12\">${next}</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk11\">right-prompt</span><span class=\"mtk1\">() {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk4\">local</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> time=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;%F{242}%T%f&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk11\">echo</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk12\">${time}</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">PROMPT=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">`left-prompt`</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">RPROMPT=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">`right-prompt`</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk11\">unset</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> -f left-prompt</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk11\">unset</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> -f right-prompt</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>関数の宣言もスクリプトローカルにしたかったのだけど、やり方がわからなかった。<br>\nひとまず最後に<code>unset</code>するとこで同じ結果は得られるのでそうした。</p>\n<h2 id=\"参考\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83\" aria-label=\"参考 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline; fill: #57606a;\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>参考</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://tegetegekibaru.blogspot.com/2012/08/zsh_2.html\">zsh 設定 - プロンプト -</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://chirashi.twittospia.com/%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93/macos%E3%82%BF%E3%83%BC%E3%83%9F%E3%83%8A%E3%83%AB%E3%81%A7zsh%E3%83%97%E3%83%AD%E3%83%B3%E3%83%97%E3%83%88%E3%82%92%E3%82%AB%E3%82%B9%E3%82%BF%E3%83%9E%E3%82%A4%E3%82%BA%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B%E6%96%B9/2021-02-13/\">macOS ターミナルで zsh プロンプトをカスタマイズする方法</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://dev.macha795.com/zsh-prompt-customize/\">zsh プロンプトをカスタマイズ、色と改行と git 対応で見やすくする【Mac】</a></li>\n</ul>\n<style class=\"grvsc-styles\">\n  .grvsc-container {\n    overflow: auto;\n    position: relative;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    padding-top: 1rem;\n    padding-top: var(--grvsc-padding-top, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    padding-bottom: 1rem;\n    padding-bottom: var(--grvsc-padding-bottom, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    border-radius: var(--grvsc-border-radius, 8px);\n    font-feature-settings: normal;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-code {\n    display: table;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line {\n    display: table-row;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    width: 100%;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line > * {\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter-pad {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter {\n    display: table-cell;\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter::before {\n    content: attr(data-content);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 1.5rem;\n    padding-left: var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n    padding-right: 1.5rem;\n    padding-right: var(--grvsc-padding-right, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source:empty::after {\n    content: ' ';\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter + .grvsc-source {\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  /* Line transformer styles */\n  \n  .grvsc-has-line-highlighting > .grvsc-code > .grvsc-line::before {\n    content: ' ';\n    position: absolute;\n    width: 100%;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-add::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-add-background-color, rgba(0, 255, 60, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-del::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-del-background-color, rgba(255, 0, 20, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-number {\n    padding: 0 2px;\n    text-align: right;\n    opacity: 0.7;\n  }\n  \n  .default-dark {\n    background-color: #1E1E1E;\n    color: #D4D4D4;\n  }\n  .default-dark .mtk3 { color: #6A9955; }\n  .default-dark .mtk1 { color: #D4D4D4; }\n  .default-dark .mtk8 { color: #CE9178; }\n  .default-dark .mtk11 { color: #DCDCAA; }\n  .default-dark .mtk4 { color: #569CD6; }\n  .default-dark .mtk12 { color: #9CDCFE; }\n  .default-dark .mtk6 { color: #D7BA7D; }\n  .default-dark .mtk15 { color: #C586C0; }\n  .default-dark .mtk7 { color: #B5CEA8; }\n  .default-dark .grvsc-line-highlighted::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-background-color, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1));\n    box-shadow: inset var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-width, 4px) 0 0 0 var(--grvsc-line-highlighted-border-color, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5));\n  }\n</style>","fields":{"slug":"/blog/2022/zsh-prompt-custom/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"zshプロンプトをカスタマイズする","description":null,"postdate":"2022-04-07T15:46:00","update":"2022-04-07T15:46:00","tags":["Zsh"]}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2022/gatsby-site-create-log10/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"10.Github Pagesでデプロイとアナリティクスとサイトマップ (Gatsby-jsによるサイト構築記録)"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2022/nvim-checkhealth-path/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[Neo